            <h4 class="avatar-tiny"><a href="//beta.slashdot.org/~scorp1us" class="author" title="author name and user ID">scorp1us (235526) </a> | about 2 years ago | <a href="//beta.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=3148631&cid=41478329">(#41478329)</a></h4>
        </header>
        <div id="comment_body_41478329" class="comment-wrapper" data-points="4" data-reason="Insightful">
            <div class="comment-body"><p>It's not like *real* money that you can just print out of thin air.</p><p>You've got to come up with that some how, and at $10 (so I don't need a calculator) that's $240,000 you've got to come up with.  That's a lot of mining or fees at $0.10 each. That's hard to make up with low volume of trades.</p></div>
